            <componentInstanceProperties>
                <name>richTextValue</name>
                <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(107, 109, 112);&quot;&gt;Tours &amp;amp; Tasting Guidelines for Sales&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(107, 109, 112);&quot;&gt;This pertains to all visit requests for Rutherford Hill, Chimney Rock, Maxville,&amp;nbsp;Sanford,&amp;nbsp;Rochioli and Hanna.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(107, 109, 112);&quot;&gt;Please&amp;nbsp;encourage weekday visits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(107, 109, 112);&quot;&gt;Only accounts that have depletions of 150 cases R12 qualify for lunches.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(107, 109, 112);&quot;&gt;If the account falls under the 150 case&amp;nbsp;requirement, please obtain approval from Chris Miller before you submit the request to&amp;nbsp;Leah.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rutherford Hill:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Winery Hours: We are open daily from 10am-4pm for Classic Bar Tastings&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;	The public tour is available 7 days per week: M-F 11:30am, 1:30pm, 3:30pm Sat-Sun 11:00am, 12:30pm, 2:00pm, 3:30pm (Should be limited to 4 people)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;	Private Tours &amp;amp; Tasting are available M-F (last appointment at 3:30pm)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Holiday Hours: We close at 2pm the day before Thanksgiving &amp;amp; Christmas&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;o	We are closed Thanksgiving, Christmas Day, New Years Day&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;o	We are open regular hours on New Years Eve&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;o	We do not accommodate Trade requests on Memorial Day weekend, Labor Day weekend, or Thanksgiving weekend. These are the 3 busiest weekends of the year and our focus is 100% on DTC. This is per Sandra LeDrew&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Maxville:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Winery Hours: Monday – Friday 10:30- 4:00. The last tour/tasting appointment at 3:00.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Holiday Hours: We are closed on New Year’s Eve, New Year’s Day, Presidents Day, Memorial Day&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Independence Day, Labor Day, Thanksgiving and the day after, Christmas Eve, Christmas Day.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rochioli:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Winery Hours: Our tasting appointment times are 10:30am, 12:30pm and 2:30pm every day. We take our last appointments for each day at 2:30pm. No Tours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Holiday Hours: Annual holiday closure is typically from December 16th – January 10th (those dates vary each year but that’s the time frame).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Winery Restrictions: Please no groups over 6 guests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Closed to the public second weekend of April and second weekend in October. Members Only.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;We do not allow dogs inside the tasting room but they are allowed outside on our patio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hanna:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tasting Room Hours: 10:30am-4:00pm. Last appointment at 2:30pm. No Tours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Holiday Hours: Closed Thanksgiving, Christmas Day and New Year’s Day.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Chimney Rock:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Winery Hours: 10:00am-4pm. Last tour at 3:30pm&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Private Tours &amp;amp; Tasting are available M-F (last appointment at 3:30pm)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Holiday Hours: Closed Thanksgiving Day, Christmas Day, New Year’s Day and Easter. We close at 2:00 pm the day prior to the holiday.&lt;/p&gt;</value>
